ntional organizing forces.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aLabor unions. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / Labor & Industrial Relations.2bisacsh  aunions, trade unions, strikes, labour force, immigrant labourers, Doug O'Halloran, XL Fine Foods.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2018z978311127363108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2018z978311127598740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781771992008423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781771992008/original  a978-3-11-127363-1  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2018b2018  a978-3-11-127598-7  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2018b2018  aGBV-deGruyter-alles